{"serial": "18003", "department_serial": 13, "code": "IL2402", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Film History", "ch": "電影史"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Wafa Ghermani"], "ch": ["倪娃法"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 3, "session": ["6", "7", "8"]}, "loc": {"building": "C2", "room": "104"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 50, "department": {"ch": "文學院學士班", "en": "Interdisciplinary Program of Liberal Arts"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "部分英語", "en": "Partially English"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 43, "selected": 0, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "This course aims at discovering the evolution of cinema : technics, trends, aesthetics that still have an influence on contemporary cinema. It will be also an opportunity to question (and contest) the evolution of film history from a very Hollywood-European centered narration to a more diverse and inclusive vision of film history. \nThe course will be bilingual in Mandarin and English.", "en": "本課程旨在發現電影的演變：仍對當代電影產生影響的技術、趨勢、美學。這也將是一個質疑（和質疑）電影史從以好萊塢-歐洲為中心的敘事到更加多樣化和包容性的電影史願景的演變的機會。 \n該課程將為普通話和英語雙語"}, "outline": {"ch": "第一週    課程介紹。\n第二週    運動影像的開始\n第三週    吸引力電影/歐洲電影的主導地位\n第四週    從東邊到西邊：美國電影的起源。\n第五週    前衛電影\n第六週    走向東方：蘇聯/日本/中國電影。有聲之前的寫實主義與前衛\n第七週    期中考\n有聲電影的發展\n第八週    好萊塢製片廠體系（以及體系外)\n第九週    動盪時期：二戰前的電影\n第十週    電影還可能像二戰前一樣嗎\n第十一週  彩色與電影\n第十二週  反叛時光 一：20 世紀 50 年代\n第十三週   反叛時光 二：1960年代的新浪潮\n第十四週   反叛時光 三： 1970年代夢想新世界\n第十五週  走向輕便：從Pathé Baby到數位相機\n第十六週  期末考", "en": "Week 1.  Class introduction\nWeek 2.   The beginning of moving image\nWeek 3   The Cinema of attraction/ The dominance of Europe\nWeek 4.    From East to West : The Beginning of cinema in the USA\nWeek 5.    The Avant-Garde cinema\nWeek 6.    Go East : Soviet / Japanese / Chinese cinemas. Realism and avant-garde before sound\nWeek 7.    Mid-term exam\nThe development of sound cinema\nWeek 8.   The Hollywood Studio System (and the outsiders)\nWeek 9.  A Time of turmoil : cinema before World War II\nWeek 10.   After World War II is cinema still possible ? despair and reconstruction\nWeek 11. Colour and films\nWeek 12. A Time for rebellion 1: The 1950s\nWeek 13.  A Time for rebellion 2: the New Waves of the 1960s\nWeek 14. A Time for rebellion : The 1970s Dreaming a new world\nWeek 15.  Going lighter : from Pathé Baby to digital camera\nWeek 16.  Final exam"}, "textbook": {"ch": "Reading provided by the professor", "en": "Reading provided by the professor"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "0", "en": "0"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "每週作業50％，期中分組口頭報告20％，期末個人書面報告30％。", "en": "每週作業50％，期中分組口頭報告20％，期末個人書面報告30％。"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "待定", "en": "待定"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "影像", "en": "影像"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "人文實踐", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "批判思考", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "多元敘事", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試"]}, {"competencies": "跨域學習", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "組織合作", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "人文實踐", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "批判思考", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "多元敘事", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam"]}, {"competencies": "跨域學習", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Practices/Experiments", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "組織合作", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": 